In 2026, custom bridge networks provide automatic DNS-based container discovery. IEEE benchmarks: bridge at 20-35 Gbps, 15-50us latency. Cilium 1.20.0 uses eBPF for container networking without kernel modules. IPvlan is now a common macvlan alternative for homelabs.

